Module org.phenopackets.phenopackettools.validator.core
Package org.phenopackets.phenopackettools.validator.core

Interface ValidationResults

public interface ValidationResults
ValidationResults contain validation results for one Phenopacket schema top-level element (Phenopacket, Family, or Cohort).

The results contain info regarding which validators were run (validators()) and the issues found during the validation (validationResults()).
